		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Wow, thanks guys!  <img src="./images/smilies/Mfr_icon_homebrew.png" alt=":beer:" title="Beer" /> <br /><br />temporary blurb in case anyone needs a reference:<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">In the dystopian wasteland <br />of Neo Hong Kong, help Blue<br />escape from the evil <br />clutches of the Omnicorp <br />conglomerate.<br /><br />Avoid robots, lasers, pools <br />of toxic waste, and more as<br />you fight your way out of a <br />research facility and exact <br />revenge upon your captors. <br /><br />CONTROLS:<br />========<br />A to jump<br />B to fire projectiles<br /><br />Ladders can be climbed, latched onto, or dropped from. <br /><br />BONUS ITEMS:<br />=========<br />-CENTS - collect a hundred to gain an extra life<br />-POWER UP - increases your shooting power until you game over<br />-HEALTH UP - increases your maximum heart gauge until you game over. <br /></div>

		

